name: salaries.Rk
description: the ranking of salary for each player in this team
explanation:
this number shows the ranking for this specific player
                  in this team

name: salaries.Player
description:
the name of player corresponding to this salary
                  in this team
explanation:
this is the name of the player who earns this salary in
                 this team

name: salaries.Salary
description: the salary of this player in this team
explanation:
this is the actual salary the player earns in this team,
                 unit is U.S. dollars
